schools.name: Clifford O. Pete Findlay Middle School

data.description: This single story home sits in a gate community in North Las Vegas with beautifully landscaped parks and walking trails. It offers new flooring throughout and newly painted bedrooms. It has 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, vaulted ceilings, a fireplace, pot shelves, and recessed lighting in the kitchen. Large Primary bedroom with ensuite bath with dual sinks, shower/tub combo, large walk in closet and separated from the other bedrooms. Separate laundry room with cabinets. Attached garage with shelving. Fully fenced backyard with a covered patio and shed.  Both front and backyard are landscaped. Plenty of nearby shopping & dining and minutes from I-215 and the I-15.
